description: Caveman Truck  is one of the first paleo / primal food truck concepts in the nation. Menus items rotate based on attainability of high quality food. Current offerings include: Bacon Hash- Organic Sweet Potato/ Organic Bacon/ Organic SausageVeg Hash- Organic Sweet Potato/ Organic Coconut OilPaleo Taco - Organic Sausage/ Organic Cucumber/ Organic Carrot/ Organic Mango/ Jicama Tortilla Barnyard Chili- Grassfed Beef/Organic Sausage/ Pastured Pork Bacon/ Organic Tomato/ Organic Sweet PotatoEggs- Pastured Chickens Raised Locally (Homestead Heritage)Paleo Taco (breakfast style)- Organic Sausage / Egg/ Organic Sweet PotatoSausage- Organic Pasture Raised Heritage Hogs Raised Regionally (Blackbird Heritage)drinks- bottled water & sparkling waterSome planned items include:Grassfed beef / Bison burgers / salads / sweet potato fries / bbq pulled pork / coconut water / kombucha / tea
